📘 College Student Management System – SQL Project
📌 Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing a College Student Management System using SQL.
It involves working with student data, course details, and marks to perform various queries such as filtering, sorting, and aggregation.

🗂️ Database Schema

The project consists of three main tables:

1. Students Table

Stores student information.

student_id (Primary Key)
student_name
gender
city
join_year
2. Courses Table

Stores course details.

course_id (Primary Key)
course_name
department
3. Marks Table

Stores student marks.

mark_id (Primary Key)
student_id (Foreign Key)
course_id (Foreign Key)
marks
⚙️ Setup Instructions
Step 1: Create Tables

Run the SQL scripts to create:

students
courses
marks
